snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Deathwatch - Tyranid Invasion [Trailer]
snippet.description:
Warhammer 40,000: Deathwatch: Tyranid Invasion is a turn-based strategy game, set on the edge of Imperial space, where your Space Marines will take on the Tyranids in a series of tactical engagements.

Available now on the Apple App Store:
http://itunes.apple.com/app/id791134629
